to the Secretariat of the CCNR. It should be sent for the attention of the Human Resources Officer, Caroline Leris, (tel. +33 (0)3 88 52 20 12,
career@ccr-zkr.org
) who will also be able to answer any questions on the recruitment procedure;
For more information about the tasks associated with this position, please visit our website
www.ccr-zkr.org
or contact Raphaël Wisselmann, Chief Engineer, (tel. +33 (0)3 88 52 20 09,
r.wisselmann@ccr-zkr.org
).
