We are looking for a project manager to join the Business Strategy and Project Management (BSPM) division to strengthen the European Stability Mechanism’s (ESM) artificial intelligence (AI) capabilities and contribute to a broader portfolio of strategic and business change initiatives. The division leads strategy implementation and business change through analysis, disciplined project execution, and quality management to help achieve corporate goals.
