This role would suit a person with strong pitching skills, who is interested in developing their grant application skillset and is highly motivated by our mission. The
Grants Intern
will be part of the Operations & Projects department of Finance Watch, comprising Finance, HR & Operations.
The
Grants Intern
will report to the Head of Communications & Operations and work closely with the whole team on a daily basis.
